// Dragnet [Container]: dragnet-container-2024-0351 — Vulnerable Base Image Pull
// Status: deprecated | Level: critical | ID: 9bf2b63a-f18d-51fa-8435-4c36112c6cb5

any where
  (process.executable like~ "*debian:11*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:12*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:13*" or process.executable like~ "*debian:14*")
